Fle3 is a Learning Environment
==============================
Website: http://fle3.uiah.fi/


Fle3 is: 

*  www-based platform for computer supported collaborative learning (CSCL). 
*  supports on-line learning community and teamwork (groupware).
*  server-based application and database.
*  Cross-platform for end users (www-browser in Linux, Mac, Win PC, WebTV,
   Nokia Communicator, etc).
*  is NOT a distance education system, but one which supports real live
   class situations with net based learning tools.


For installation instructions please consult the INSTALL file.

